InternetSharing(8) System Manager's Manual InternetSharing(8)

NAME

InternetSharing — daemon for Internet Sharing.

SYNOPSIS

NONE (launched by launchd)

DESCRIPTION

InternetSharing is a system daemon which sets up Internet Sharing.

This command is not intended to be invoked directly.

FILES

/usr/libexec/InternetSharing
 

SEE ALSO

launchd(8)
